-- Kumba Says ArcelorMittal South Africa Arbitration May Take a `Year Or Two'
-- Ron Derby
-- 2010-07-22T08:54:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/kumba-says-arcelormittal-south-africa-arbitration-may-take-a-year-or-two-.html

          
          
             The arbitration process between
Kumba Iron Ore Ltd. and ArcelorMittal South Africa Ltd. to
resolve a disputed iron ore supply agreement may take a “year
or two,” Kumba Chief Executive Officer Chris Griffith said in
Johannesburg today.  
